      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2019-05-13</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-01-30T23:18:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Construction Consensus Procurement Improvement Act of</strong> <b>2019</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the use of reverse auctions for awarding federal contracts for construction and design services. Generally, a reverse auction is one in which there are multiple sellers lowering their bids to win a supply or service contract.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
